d locally at the oxidation sites, and causing\nthe transition of the backbone conformations from BI to BII at the regions of\noxidative damage.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2022 11:53:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-19"}
