 spiking graph neural network with\nLLIF neurons. Extensive experiments demonstrate the significant improvements of\nour models over the state-of-the-art methods on event-driven tactile learning.\nMoreover, compared to the counterpart artificial neural networks (ANNs), our\nSNN models are 10x to 100x energy-efficient, which shows the superior energy\nefficiency of our models and may bring new opportunities to the spike-based\nlearning community and neuromorphic engineering.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 9 Oct 2022 14:49:27 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Oct 2022 02:34:25 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 19 Dec 2022 08:06:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-12-20"}
